<span class=\"diff-highlight\">within<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">a<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">cloud<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">solution<\/span> to <span class=\"diff-highlight\">an<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">engagement<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">that<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">occurs<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">in<\/span> weeks or <span class=\"diff-highlight\">in<\/span> months<span class=\"diff-highlight\">.&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"diff-highlight\">Cloud<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">infrastructure<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">means<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">that<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">organizations<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">can<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">be<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">up<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">and<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">running<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">quickly<\/span>, <span class=\"diff-highlight\">and<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">once<\/span> the <span class=\"diff-highlight\">hardware<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">and<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">infrastructure<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">are<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">established<\/span><span class=\"diff-highlight\">,<\/span> cloud <span class=\"diff-highlight\">providers<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">utilize<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">templates<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">consisting<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">of<\/span> pre-configured <span class=\"diff-highlight\">MDM<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">solutions<\/span>. <br><span class=\"diff-highlight\"><br>All<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">of<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">this<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">means<\/span> <span class=\"diff-highlight\">that<\/span> organizations <span class=\"diff-high